rComments: Easy for any ECE freshman I would say. Sometimes you don't need to go to the lecture. As long as you read all the lecture notes and do practice problems. I also registered the honor lab section and it was awesome. The lab section could be easy or hard depends on your partner.

Has a tendency during lectures to sort of try making some conceptsproblems seem easier by asserting they are not that hard. However, he is a very nice guy and really truly genuinely wants to see every student succeed. The amount of support available in the course is very high.

Prof Schmitz does a fantastic job of explaining the material. His lectures are also inspirational in that he urges and prepares you to do well in future ECE classes with little tidbits of advice he incorporates in lecture. He also stays after to answer everyone's questions.
